Review Text: I have been waiting to add this review for quite some time now. The combo from Chinese wok goes out of availability quickly and I had to struggle to order. Once I did, I understood why. The fried rice was awesome. I ordered an egg fried rice with chilli chicken combo. The price was reasonable and the taste was awesome. The quantity could have been better. Overall, I love the Chicken Fried Rice too. The packaging for non combo items is top notch. The packaging for combos could be improved.

Ordered veg Fried rice and chilli mushroom gravy 
From chinese wok
Taste 5/0
Mushrooms are my favourite but this chill mushroom gravy is the worst mushroom item i ever had.

Tried the veg spring roll and sesame chicken. Both of the items were decent in taste and pricing was decent.
The drive-in has a good option of food choices.
I ordered egg fried rice and pepper chicken...worst pepper chicken I have ever had. Egg fried rice was also very average. I don't recommend this place
Very good Chinese food. Try their rolls n prawns just out of the world. Fried rice is also very very good. Along with that thick milkshakes where nice.
